description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at how Bloodborne, the most coveted Sony exclusive to be locked away to a console. After a couple months it's almost attainable by PC gamers to preserve and enjoy through an emulator that's progressed faster than anything I've seen in a long time. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Bloodborne is Nearly Playable on PC Now...
